- [ ] **(HIGH)** Re-read every money-moving path that changed; confirm amounts flow server-side — \`src/integrations/paystack.ts:2\`
- [ ] **(HIGH)** Confirm no amount, currency, or price is trusted from the client payload — \`src/integrations/paystack.ts:2\`
- [ ] **(HIGH)** Confirm idempotency keys survive the change — a retried charge must not double-charge — \`src/integrations/paystack.ts:2\`
- [ ] **(HIGH)** Confirm provider errors are mapped deliberately (no silent swallow, no raw leak to the client) — \`src/integrations/paystack.ts:2\`
